Package com.ephesoft.dcma.imagemagick.imageClassifier

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayListErrorConsumer
    This class is an ErrorConsumer which saves the Error to an ArrayList.
    ImageClassifier
    This class contains the functionality to classify images based on the sample images kept in the sampleBaseFolderPath.
    ImageComparisonUtil
    This class contains methods to compare two images.The underlying engine to compare images is Image Magick.One of the method uses IM4Java to talk to Image Magick.
    SampleConfidenceBean
    This bean simply maintains the.SamplePageName and the confidence score.
    SampleThumbnailGenerator
    This Class generates thumbnails for all folders located at the folder location specified by the property imagemagick.sample_base_folder_path of the property file imagemagick.properties.
